---
// You can keep the array empty for now if you are hardcoding the divs below
const workflow = []; 
---

<section id="workflow" class="py-24 border-t border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Design <span class="text-indigo-500">Workflow</span></h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-xl">My systematic approach to turning abstract ideas into production-ready applications.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="group p-8 bg-indigo-500/5 border border-indigo-500/10 rounded-3xl hover:bg-indigo-500/10 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-400 font-black mb-6">01</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Wireframe</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Mapping user flows and data architecture in Figma to ensure logical clarity before coding.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="group p-8 bg-cyan-500/5 border border-cyan-500/10 rounded-3xl hover:bg-cyan-500/10 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-cyan-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-cyan-400 font-black mb-6">02</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Prototype</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Creating high-fidelity interactions and motion systems to test the user experience "feel."</p>
            </div>

            <div class="group p-8 bg-purple-500/5 border border-purple-500/10 rounded-3xl hover:bg-purple-500/10 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 font-black mb-6">03</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Deployment</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Writing clean, modular code with Python backends and optimized Astro frontends.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>